Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:33.18,Dragner edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-35\fad(150,150)\pos(565.2,1077)}{\blur7}BOMB！BOMB！煩悩ばっか増殖？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:33.18,Dragner edchbig5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-35\fad(150,150)\pos(1464.533,8.6)}{\blur7}BOMB BOMB 煩惱不斷增殖？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:36.27,Dragner edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}マニッシュな裏に 垣間見せる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:36.27,Dragner edchbig5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}窺視男性化的背後的縫隙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:39.64,Dragner edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}ガーリーなチェリッシュ 如何ほど？
