Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:39.85,Dragner edchbig5,,0,0,0,,{\frz-35\fad(150,150)\pos(1640,5.266)}{\blur7}CAN'T YOU FEEL?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.94,Dragner edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}自分のコトノハで云わなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.94,Dragner edchbig5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}必須是出自肺腑之言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:44.77,Dragner edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}「賛成！」「酸性？」「中性？」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:44.77,Dragner edchbig5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}「贊成！」「酸性？」「中性？」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:48.90,Dragner edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}「アンタ、それでも　ホモサピエンス！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:48.90,Dragner edchbig5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}「你這樣也算理性的人嗎！？」
